title: paintingAwarenessSuccess
---
[nomarkup][The vibrantly colored soup of mismatched geometric shapes is nauseating, but you manage to see past that. You reach up to dislodge the panels in the polyptych. Youe see that something is hidden behind it, because shadow neat the frame isn't going in straight line. Applying a modest amount of force to the largest painting in the center unlatches it, revealing a safe on the wall. There is also a paper stamp on the back of the canvas.][/nomarkup] #success
===
title: successContinued
---
<<set $safeDiscovered to true>>
-> Continue
<<if GetIsPartyMemberRecruited($anastasia) is true>>
