title: paintingIntelligenceSuccess
---
[nomarkup][Those are hideous pieces of art, but still - you recognize that this particular set looks like it is worth quite a bit. It had to be bought in one of the local galleries or on an auction. Such pieces often have stamps or notes on their back. It may even contain some useful information. Like when or where this set was bought. You stare at the picture which seems to be made under the acid influence for a minute and then dislodge it from the wall and look at it's back. You are not disappointed - indeed there is a paper stamp... and the safe.][/nomarkup] #success
<<set $safeDiscovered to true>>
<<jump successContinued>>
===
title: paintingWitsSuccess
---
[nomarkup][This painting is here on purpose. It's not a simple wall decoration. It's here for a reason. It just doesn't sit with Diana proudly painting herself as a british punk rocker. Otherwise she'd just place Sex Pistols or The Exploited posters on the wall. Maybe there's something worth looking for behind one part of this poliptich? You go with your gut, and dislodge one of the paintings. You were right. There's a paper stamp on the back. And the safe...][/nomarkup] #success
<<set $safeDiscovered to true>>
<<jump successContinued>>
