title: anaAndKieranConflict
---
[nomarkup][you see that Kieran will continue and you get a feeling that if you don't stop them both they will just argue till dawn catches you here][/nomarkup]
{$innerVoice}: Shit...
{$beast}: If they won't stop I'm gonna be dead...
-> {$pcName}: Listen guys... BOTH of you. It's my investigation and we'll do as I say alright? It's not only his ass on the line, but mine too.
    [nomarkup][Anastasia and Kieran focus on you, then stare at each other][/nomarkup]
    {$kieran}: We'll end this conversation at another time.
    {$anastasia}: I'll hold you to that. I'm eager to crush all your stupid arguments to dust.
-> {$pcName}: Kieran, do you really want to roll around in her mud till dawn?
    [nomarkup][Kieran looks at you and shooks his head][/nomarkup]
    {$kieran}: You're right. It's not a good place or time for a philosophical discussion. \[+1 Kieran influence\]
    <<ModifyInfluence (+1,$kieran)>>
    [nomarkup][Anastasia frowns at you][/nomarkup]
    {$anastasia}: MY mud? It's him who didn't tell you about the Beast in the first place! \[-1 Anastasia influence\]
    <<ModifyInfluence (-1,$anastasia)>>
-> {$pcName}: Shut up Kieran! For a guy who tells me he's here to help you hide a lot from me!
    {$anastasia}: Yes! Exactly my thought! \[+1 Anastasia Influence\]
    <<ModifyInfluence (+1,$anastasia)>>
    {$kieran}: I'm sorry, okay? There was too little time to tell you everything... \[-1 Kieran influence\]
    <<ModifyInfluence (-1,$kieran)>>
